<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(ii)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 18PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive&#x2019;s material violation of a Company policy (including any insider trading policy) or any written agreement or covenant with the Company;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 10PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:10PT;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(iii)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 14.4PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive&#x2019;s conviction of, or entry of a plea of guilty or
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	nolo contendere
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	to, a felony (other than motor vehicle offenses the effect of which do not materially impair Executive&#x2019;s performance of his employment duties);
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 10PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:10PT;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(iv)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 18PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	a willful act by Executive that constitutes gross misconduct and which is injurious to the Company;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 10PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:10PT;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(v)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 21.6PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive&#x2019;s commission of any act of fraud, embezzlement, dishonesty or any other willful misconduct that has caused or is reasonably expected to result in material injury to the Company;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 10PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:10PT;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(vi)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 18PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	the unauthorized use or disclosure by Executive of any proprietary information or trade secrets of the Company or any other party to whom Executive owes an obligation of nondisclosure as a result of Executive&#x2019;s relationship with the Company; or
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 10PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:10PT;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(vii)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 14.4PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive&#x2019;s willful failure to cooperate with an investigation by a governmental authority.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 10PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:10PT;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	The determination as to whether Executive is being terminated for Cause will be made in good faith by the Board and will be final and binding on Executive. The foregoing definition does not in any way limit the Company&#x2019;s ability to terminate Executive&#x2019;s employment relationship at any time as provided in Section&nbsp;2 above, and the term &#x201C;Company&#x201D; will be interpreted to include any subsidiary, parent, affiliate or successor thereto, if applicable.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 10PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:10PT;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 36PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(b)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 21.6PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Change
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	in
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Control.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;&#x201C;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	Change
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	in
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	Control
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201D; means the occurrence of any of the following events:
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 36PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 10PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:10PT;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(i)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 21.6PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	A change in the ownership of the Company which occurs on the date that any one person, or more than one person acting as a group (&#x201C;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	Person
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201D;), acquires ownership of the stock of the Company that, together with the stock held by such Person, constitutes more than
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	thirty
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	percent (
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	3
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	0%)&nbsp;of the total voting power of the stock of the Company; provided, however, that for purposes of this subsection, the acquisition of additional stock by any one Person, who is considered to own more than
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	thirty
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	percent (
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	3
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	0%)&nbsp;of the total voting power of the stock of the Company will not be considered a Change
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	in
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Control; or
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 4PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:4PT;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">

<P STYLE="PAGE-BREAK-AFTER:ALWAYS">
	&nbsp;
</P>
<A NAME="eolPage107"></A>
</DIV>
<DIV STYLE="MARGIN-LEFT:5.88235294117647%;MARGIN-RIGHT:5.88235294117647%;">
</DIV>
<DIV STYLE="MARGIN-LEFT:5.88235294117647%;MARGIN-RIGHT:5.88235294117647%;">
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(ii)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 18PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	A change in the effective control of the Company which occurs on the date that a majority of members of the Board is replaced during any twelve (12)&nbsp;month period by Directors whose appointment or election is not endorsed by a majority of the members of the Board prior to the date of the appointment or election. For purposes of this clause (ii), if any Person is considered to be in effective control of the Company, the acquisition of additional control of the Company by the same Person will not be considered a Change
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	in
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Control; or
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(iii)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 14.4PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	A change in the ownership of a substantial portion of the Company&#x2019;s assets which occurs on the date that any Person acquires (or has acquired during the twelve (12)&nbsp;month period ending on the date of the most recent acquisition by such
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	P
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	erson or
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	P
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	ersons)&nbsp;assets from the Company that have a total gross fair market value equal to or more than fifty percent (50%)&nbsp;of the total gross fair market value of all of the assets of the Company immediately prior to such acquisition or acquisitions; provided, however, that for purposes of this subsection (iii), the following will not constitute a change in the ownership of a substantial portion of the Company&#x2019;s assets: (A)&nbsp;a transfer to an entity that is controlled by the Company&#x2019;s stockholders immediately after the transfer, or (B)&nbsp;a transfer of assets by the Company to: (1)&nbsp;a stockholder of the Company (immediately before the asset transfer)&nbsp;in exchange for or with respect to the Company&#x2019;s stock, (2)&nbsp;an entity, fifty percent (50%)&nbsp;or more of the total value or voting power of which is owned, directly or indirectly, by the Company, (3)&nbsp;a Person, that owns, directly or indirectly,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	more than
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	thirty
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	percent (
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	3
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	0%)&nbsp; of the total value or voting power of all the outstanding stock of the Company, or (4)&nbsp;an entity, at least fifty percent (50%)&nbsp;of the total value or voting power of which is owned, directly or indirectly, by a Person described in this subsection (iii)(B)(3). For purposes of this subsection (iii), gross fair market value means the value of the assets of the Company, or the value of the assets being disposed of, determined without regard to any liabilities associated with such assets.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	For purposes of this definition,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	P
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	ersons will be considered to be acting as a group if they are owners of a corporation that enters into a merger, consolidation, purchase or acquisition of stock, or similar business transaction with the Company. Further and for the avoidance of doubt, a transaction will not constitute a Change
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	in
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Control if: (i)&nbsp;its sole purpose is to change the state of the Company&#x2019;s incorporation, or (ii)&nbsp;its sole purpose is to create a holding company that will be owned in substantially the same proportions by the
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	P
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	ersons who held the Company&#x2019;s securities immediately before such transaction.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 36PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(c)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 21.6PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Change
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	in
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Control Period
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	. &#x201C;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	Change
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	in
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	Control Period
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201D; will mean the period beginning two (2)&nbsp;months prior to, and ending
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	twenty-
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	four
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	2
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	4
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	)&nbsp;months following, a Change
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	in
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Control.

</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 36PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;

<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 36PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(d)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 21.6PT 0PT 0PT;">

	Code
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	Code
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201D; will mean the Internal Revenue Code of 1986, as amended.

<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 36PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(e)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 21.6PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Disability
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	. &#x201C;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	Disability
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201D; will mean that Executive has been unable to engage in any substantial gainful activity by reason of any medically determinable physical or mental impairment that can be expected to result in death or can be expected to last for a continuous period of not less than twelve (12)&nbsp;months. Alternatively, Executive will be deemed disabled if determined to be totally disabled by the Social Security Administration. Termination resulting from Disability may only be effected after at least thirty (30)&nbsp;days&#x2019; written notice by the Company of its intention to terminate Executive&#x2019;s employment. In the event that
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 36PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201D; will mean two (2)&nbsp;times the lesser of: (i)&nbsp;Executive&#x2019;s annualized compensation based upon the annual rate of pay paid to Executive during Executive&#x2019;s taxable year preceding Executive&#x2019;s taxable year of Executive&#x2019;s termination of employment as determined under, and with such adjustments as are set forth in, Treasury Regulation 1.409A-1(b)(9)(iii)(A)(1)&nbsp;and any Internal Revenue Service guidance issued with respect thereto; or (ii)&nbsp;the maximum amount that may be taken into account under a qualified plan pursuant to Section&nbsp;401(a)(17)&nbsp;of the Code for the year in which Executive&#x2019;s employment is terminated.

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 21.6PT 0PT 0PT;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	The Company&#x2019;s Successors
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	. Any successor to the Company (whether direct or indirect and whether by purchase, merger, consolidation, liquidation or otherwise)&nbsp;to all or substantially all of the Company&#x2019;s business and/or assets will assume the obligations under this Agreement and agree expressly to perform the obligations under this Agreement in the same manner and to the same extent as the Company would be required to perform such obligations in the absence of a succession. For all purposes under this Agreement, the term &#x201C;Company&#x201D; will include any successor to the Company&#x2019;s business and/or assets which executes and delivers the assumption agreement described in this Section&nbsp;7(a) or which becomes bound by the terms of this Agreement by operation of law.
</FONT>
</P>

<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(a)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 21.6PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	General
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	. Notices and all other communications contemplated by this Agreement will be in writing and will be deemed to have been duly given when sent electronically or personally delivered
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	when mailed by U.S. registered or certified mail, return receipt requested and postage prepaid
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	or when delivered by a private courier service such as UPS, DHL or Federal Express that has tracking capability. In the case of Executive, notices will be sent to the e-mail address or addressed to Executive at the home address, in either case which Executive most recently communicated to the Company in writing. In the case of the Company, electronic notices will be sent to the e-mail address of the Chief Executive Officer
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	or
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	the General Counsel and mailed notices will be addressed to its corporate headquarters, and all notices will be directed to the attention of its Chief Executive Officer
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	or
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	General Counsel.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 36PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Notice of Termination
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	. Any termination by the Company for Cause or by Executive for Good Reason will be communicated by a notice of termination to the other party hereto given in accordance with Section&nbsp;8(a) of this Agreement. Such notice will indicate the specific termination provision in this Agreement relied upon, will set forth in reasonable detail the facts and circumstances claimed to provide a basis for termination under the provision so indicated, and will specify the termination date (which will be not more than ninety (90)&nbsp;days after the giving of such notice).
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 36PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">

</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	. Upon the termination of Executive&#x2019;s employment for any reason, Executive will be deemed to have resigned from all officer and/or director positions held at the Company and its affiliates&nbsp;voluntarily, without any further required action by Executive, as of the end of Executive&#x2019;s employment
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	,

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	and Executive, at the Board&#x2019;s request, will execute any documents reasonably necessary to reflect Executive&#x2019;s resignation.

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	and the Company wish to end their at-will employment relationship
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">

</FONT>

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	and the Company, for the good and valuable consideration stated below, the sufficiency of which is acknowledged, agree as follows:

</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;COLOR:#000000;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	1.

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">

</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">

</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">

</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">

</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">

</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">

</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">

</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">

<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;COLOR:#000000;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	in Employment Act of 1967, as amended, the Company&#x2019;s obligations under this Agreement
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	and the CIC Agreement
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	will become null and void.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;COLOR:#000000;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	8.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	agrees that
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	will not, in any way, disparage the Company
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	or any of the Released Parties.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Further,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	and the Company agree that they will not make, nor solicit, any comments, statements, or the like to the media, or to others, that may be considered to be derogatory or detrimental to the good name or business reputation of
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	or the Company.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	9.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	acknowledges that, through
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x2019;s employment with the Company,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	has acquired and had access to the Company&#x2019;s confidential and proprietary business information and trade secrets (&#x201C;Confidential Information&#x201D;).&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	acknowledges and agrees that the Company prohibits the use or disclosure of its Confidential Information and that the Company has taken all reasonable steps necessary to protect the secrecy of such Confidential Information.&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	acknowledges and agrees that &#x201C;Confidential Information&#x201D; includes any data or information that is valuable to the Company and not generally known to competitors of the Company or other outsiders, regardless of whether the confidential information is in printed, written or electronic form, retained in
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x2019;s memory or has been compiled or created by
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	, including but not limited to: business plans; product designs, drawings and formulas; test and development data; customer or prospective customer, vendor, supplier and distributor information; financial information; marketing strategies; pending projects and proposals; personnel and payroll records; pricing data; contract terms; proprietary production processes; third party information that
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	the Company has
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	a duty to maintain as confidential; and other business-related information, which, if made available to
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	the Company&#x2019;s
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	competitors or the public, would be advantageous to such competitors
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	and detrimental to the Company.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	agrees that
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	has not and in the future will not use, or disclose to any third party, Confidential Information, unless compelled by law after reasonable advance notice to the Company, and further agrees to return all documents, disks, CDs, DVDs, drives, storage devices or any other item or source containing Confidential Information, or
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	any other of the Company&#x2019;s property, to the Company up
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	on execution of this Agreement.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	If
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	has any question regarding what data or information would be considered by the Company to be Confidential Information subject to this provision,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	agrees to contact ______________________________________ _______________________________________
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	10.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	This Agreement contains the complete understanding between the parties, with the sole and limited exception of the
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	CIC Ag
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	reement and the Non-Compete,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	Non-Solicitation and Confidentiality agreement between the Company and Executive dated the same
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	date as the CIC Agreement
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	, which shall remain in full force and effect.&nbsp;&nbsp;The parties agree that no promises or agreements will be binding or will modify this understanding unless in writing and signed by both parties.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	11.

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive

	), are incorporated into this Agreement and shall apply to any alleged or actual breaches of this Agreement or any other claims arising out of
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s employment with the Company and its affiliates that are not otherwise released by this Agreement.&nbsp;

<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;">
	&nbsp;

<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	A.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	The Company and its Affiliates are engaged in the business of selling, distributing and installing a wide range of products for new
</FONT>
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_1_8">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">

</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	existing
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	home improvement projects throughout the United States, including, but not limited to insulation,
</FONT>
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_1_12">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	gutters, fireplaces and fire doors
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	The Company&#x2019;s business depends upon the preservation of goodwill and continued confidentiality of proprietary information and trade secrets.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	1.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 28.8PT 0PT 0PT;">

<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	the public other than as a result of disclosure by
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	2.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 28.8PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	Restricted Use of Confidential Information
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;In the course of
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s employment,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	will have access to and may help develop
</FONT>
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_2_34">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Confidential Information. Except as required in the performance of
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s duties
</FONT>
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_1_37">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	, &nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	will not, either
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	during
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s employment or at any time thereafter,
</FONT>
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_1_39">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	disclose any
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Confidential Information to others or use the Confidential Information for
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s own benefit or for the benefit of others.&nbsp;&nbsp;All records, files, and documents relating to the Company&#x2019;s business shall remain the sole property of the Company
</FONT>
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_1_45">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	and
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	may not be cop
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	ied without written permission.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Upon the termination of
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s employment,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	agrees to promptly return all records, files, documents and other materials relating to the Company&#x2019;s business, whether in hard copy or electronic format.&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	shall not retain copies of such materials.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	3.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 28.8PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Nothing in this Agreement shall be construed to limit
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s right to
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	respond accurately and fully to any question, inquiry or request for information when required by legal process or
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	from initiating communications directly with, or responding to any inquiry from, or providing testimony before, any self-regulatory organization or state or federal regulatory authority, regarding the Company,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive&#x2019;s
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	employment, or this Agreement.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	is not required to contact the Company regarding the subject matter of any such communications before engaging in such communications
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	NON-SOLICITATION AND NON-COMPETITION
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	4.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 28.8PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	Need for Covenants
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	E
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	xecutive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	understands that the Company has spent and will continue to spend substantial amounts of time, money and effort to develop its business, Confidential Information, reputation, goodwill (both associated with it trade name and geographic area of business), and&nbsp;&nbsp;its customer, supplier and employee relationships.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	further understands that
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	will benefit from those investments and efforts.&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	acknowledges
</FONT>
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_1_53">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	that
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s use of any such matters
</FONT>
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_1_57">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	to compete against the Company in an unrestricted manner would be unfair
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	and detrimental to the Company.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	agrees that taking advantage of any of the above-identified investments of time, money or effort expended by the Company would unfairly place the
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	at a competitive advantage over Company.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	further acknowledges the Company&#x2019;s need to protect its business interests by reasonably restricting
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s ability to compete with the Company.&nbsp;&nbsp;Finally,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	acknowledges that the Company would not employ, or continue to employ,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	, or enter into the CIC Agreement,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	without
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s agreement to be bound by the provisions of this Agreement.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	5.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 28.8PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	Definitions
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(a)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201C;Affiliate&#x201D; means, as to any person or entity, any other person or entity (i) that directly or indirectly controls, is controlled by, or is under direct or indirect common control with, such person or entity or (ii) that has the power directly or indirectly to direct or cause the direction of the management and policies of such person or entity, through the ownership of voting securities, by contract or otherwise.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_1_63">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(b)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201C;Competitive Capacity&#x201D; means performing the same or similar duties as those performed by
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	on behalf of the Company at any time during the 24 month period preceding the date of
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x2019;s termination of employment.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">

<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(c)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201C;Competitive Products&#x201D; means any product or service offered by the Company in the Territory or any product or service that directly or indirectly competes with or is substantially similar to such product or service. For illustrative purposes, these products may include insulation distribution and installation.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(d)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201C;Competitor&#x201D; means any person or entity (including Executive or an entity that Executive becomes affiliated with or renders services to) that offers, or is actively planning to offer, Competitive Products within the Territory.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(e)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201C;Customer&#x201D; means all customers and actively sought prospective customers of the Company with whom Executive had material contact in the performance of Executive&#x2019;s duties at any time during the 24 month period preceding the date of Executive&#x2019;s termination of employment.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(f)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201C;Territory&#x201D; means the United States of America.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(g)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201C;Restricted Period&#x201D; means the period of Executive&#x2019;s employment with the Company or an Affiliate and for a period of 18 months following date of Executive&#x2019;s termination of employment for any reason, whether voluntary or involuntary.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	(h)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;">
	&#x201C;Directly or indirectly&#x201D; means conduct taken individually, through other individuals, or as a partner, shareholder, member, officer, director, manager, employee, salesperson, independent contractor, agent, or consultant for any other individual or entity.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	6.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 28.8PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	Non-Solicitation/Non-Interference
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;During
</FONT>
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_1_103">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	the Restricted
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="FONT-SIZE:12PT;BORDER-BOTTOM-STYLE:SOLID;BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH:1PT;COLOR:#000000;HEIGHT:100%;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Period,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	shall not, either for
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s own account or for or on behalf of any Competitor, directly or indirectly, take any of the following actions:
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	(a)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Contact or otherwise solicit any employee, consultant, or independent contractor of the Company with the intention of encouraging such person to terminate his or her employment or other relationship with the Company, or employ or otherwise hire or engage any such person;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	(b)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Solicit, call upon, accept work and/or orders for product from, or initiate communication or contact with any Customer for the purpose of offering Competitive Products to such Customer, or otherwise offer Competitive Products to such Customer;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	(c)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Solicit, call upon or initiate communication or contact with any Customer, vendor or supplier of the Company for the purpose of encouraging such person to terminate, place elsewhere or reduce the volume of its business with the Company; or
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	(d)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Otherwise attempt to directly or indirectly interfere with the Company&#x2019;s business or its relationships with its employees, independent contractors, vendors, suppliers or Customers.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>

<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	7.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 28.8PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	Non-Competition
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	During the Restricted Period,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	shall not, either for
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">

<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s own account or for or on behalf of any Competitor

<FONT STYLE="FONT-SIZE:12PT;BORDER-BOTTOM-STYLE:SOLID;BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH:1PT;COLOR:#000000;HEIGHT:100%;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;">
	,
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	directly or indirectly, take any of the following actions:
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	(a)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	(i) Have an ownership or financial interest in
</FONT>
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_1_122">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	a &nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Competitor, (ii) advise or consult with
</FONT>
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_1_124">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	a &nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Competitor concerning competitive activity in the Territory, or (iii) otherwise be employed by or provide services in a Competitive Capacity to a Competitor in the Territory;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	(b)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Engage in the production, sale or distribution of Competitive Products in the Territory; or
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	(c)
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Market, sell, or otherwise offer or provide Competitive Products in
</FONT>
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_1_129">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	the
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Territory
</FONT>
<A NAME="BLD-20151231EX10110FC1D_HTM__CP_TEXT_1_132">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	.&nbsp;

</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT 0PT 0PT 72PT;TEXT-INDENT: -36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">

<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	GENERAL PROVISIONS
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;

</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	8.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 28.8PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	Survival/Independent Agreement
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;Unless expressly set forth in a document signed by both parties, the restrictive covenants set forth herein shall survive the termination of this Agreement and the termination of
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s employment for any reason, voluntary or involuntary.&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s obligations hereunder are independent of
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s employment.&nbsp;&nbsp;Any breach or alleged breach by the Company of any obligation to
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	shall not affect the binding nature of
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s obligations under this Agreement or excuse or terminate
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&#x2019;s obligations hereunder.&nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>

<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;COLOR:#000000;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	9.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 28.8PT 0PT 0PT;">
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	Scope
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;If any provision of this Agreement is found to be invalid in any jurisdiction, in whole or in part, such provision shall remain va
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	lid in all other jurisdictions.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	If any court determines that any provision of this Agreement is unenforceable because of the duration or scope of such provision, such provision shall not be rendered void, and such court shall have the power to amend the scope or duration of such provision, and in its amended form, such provision shall remain in full force and effect.&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	If any provision of this Agreement is found to be void or unenforceable for any reason, all remaining provisions of this Agreement shall remain in full force and effect.&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp; &nbsp;
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:36PT;BORDER-TOP:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;BORDER-BOTTOM:1PT NONE #D9D9D9 ;COLOR:#000000;TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;TEXT-JUSTIFY:INTER-IDEOGRAPH;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;;FONT-SIZE: 12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN,TIMES,SERIF;TEXT-INDENT:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:0PT;PADDING:0PT 25.2PT 0PT 0PT;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">

<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;COLOR:#000000;">
	Specific Enforcement/Injunctive Relief
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	agrees that it would be difficult to measure the Company&#x2019;s damages from a breach or threatened breach of this Agreement by
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	, but that such breach or threatened breach could result in damages that would b
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	e significant and irreparable.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Executive
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	agrees that the Company shall be entitled, in addition to any other remedies available at law, to seek injunctive or other equitable relief against su
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	ch breach or threatened breach.
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	If the Company prevails in any action brought to enforce this Agreement, the Company shall be entitled to costs and attorneys&#x2019; fees incurred by it in such action.&nbsp;
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="DISPLAY:INLINE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;COLOR:#000000;">
	Notwithstanding any agreements to arbitrate disputes, the parties agree that a temporary restraining order, temporary injunctive relief, or permanent injunctive relief may be pursued and secured in court under Paragraph 10 to prevent immediate harm without waiving any party&#x2019;s ability to have all issues of final relief and damages made subject to sole and exclusive arbitration procedures.
</FONT>
</P>
